# Title: Execution Of Script Located In Potentially Suspicious Directory
# Author: Joseliyo Sanchez, @Joseliyo_Jstnk
# Date: 2023-06-02
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects executions of scripts located in potentially suspicious locations such as "/tmp" via a shell such as "bash", "sh", etc.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/process_creation/proc_creation_lnx_susp_shell_script_exec_from_susp_location.yml

CommandLine="* -c *" Image IN ("*/bash", "*/csh", "*/dash", "*/fish", "*/ksh", "*/sh", "*/zsh") CommandLine="*/tmp/*"